This is a copy of CTBN-RLE version 1.1.1 with fixes to allow it to build on a modern Debian or Ubuntu system.

To build, just run

    ./build.sh

The initial commit is from the zip file found at: http://rlair.cs.ucr.edu/ctbnrle/v1.1.1/

